cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper deals with constructing a multi-subject encoder of images to brain activity, which involves image classification, feature representations, and deep learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses learning and optimizing the aggregation of feature representations, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.NE). Additionally, the paper deals with solving for various ROIs (regions of interest) and multi-modality, which could fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
